QUIETLY
THRIVING

WITH NATASCHA HENRIKSEN

Hi there, and welcome to Quietly Thriving.

My name is Natascha Henriksen and I am a mindset + business coach for introverted women.
{" "}
After years of studying business, I started my career in the corporate world in Denmark. But a few years in human resources on the pursue to climb the corporate ladder, I realized that world wasn’t meant for me....
{" "}
In 2016 I left the corporate world, with no plan B, just a strong intuitive feeling, that something else was out there waiting for me.
{" "}
I bought a one-way ticket to Spain, to take a year off to study more and learn the language. Now, 4,5 years later I am still living and thriving in the Southern European culture.
{" "}
The years passing by in Spain, contained many ups and downs, and many different jobs along the way. All of them to confirm and enhance my strong intuitive feeling, that something just still wasn’t right.
{" "}
This started a long journey of self-reflection and self-discovery, which led me to understand, that for so long I had blamed my introverted nature for being the reason why I couldn’t get to where I wanted to be. That was so wrong! The real issue was that I had constantly been trying to live a life that wasn’t aligned with my true self.
{" "}
I made a promise to myself, to no longer pretend and hide myself. The journey did not only teach me to accept and appreciate my quiet nature, it also led the way for my career. I found my way of combining my corporate experience with my passion, and I am now on a mission to help other quiet women to unapologetically live a life that’s aligned with who they truly are.
